::Bloodystrike::

Bloodystrike jerks his head up to look at the tree as the branches 
shake, his eyes narrowing. He really wished he had his weapons right 
about now. He forces himself to relax, reminding himself that these 
bots were merchants, or so they claimed.

"Hi," he says, walking toward the tree, "I'm Bloodystrike, from the 
Alliance."
